---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Refund & Cancellation | Seetayya Foundation" description="Refund and cancellation information for Seetayya Foundation donations.">
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="container-pad max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-ink">Refund & Cancellation</h1>
      <div class="rich-content mt-8 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/74">
        <p>Donations are generally treated as voluntary support for foundation activities. Refund requests should be sent to the foundation team with the payment reference, donor name, date, and contact details.</p>
        <p>For Razorpay payments, payment status and transaction records are available through the Razorpay dashboard. For UPI or bank transfers, donors should share the transfer reference with the foundation.</p>
        <p>Before production launch, the foundation should replace this draft with its final legal refund and cancellation language.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
